# Cursor workspace

- Full architecture, invariants, and commands: root `AGENTS.md` (shared with OpenCode).
- Scoped rules in `.cursor/rules/` apply when matching files are in context; they do not replace `AGENTS.md`.
- After JS helper or Python backend changes, run `npm test` and `npm run test:python` when relevant.
- Update `AGENTS.md` when changing cross-process contracts, AI catalog pins, build inputs, or validation expectations.
- Do not add repo-root `CLAUDE.md` while using Cursor.
